              €99
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">per year</p>
            <p class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 font-semibold mt-2">Save €45 (31% off)</p>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
